data.description: Welcome to 137 Benelli Dr, located in the sought-after Hunters Ridge neighborhood in Bardstown, KY! Complete with 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, a 2 car garage and partially finished basement. This charming home offers a warm and inviting atmosphere. The spacious living area is perfect for relaxing or entertaining guests. The kitchen features modern appliances and ample cabinet space for all your culinary needs. The master bedroom comes complete with an ensuite bathroom, providing you with your own private oasis. Two additional bedrooms offer plenty of space for family or guests. One of the highlights of this property is the fully fenced backyard, offering privacy and security for children and pets to play freely. The partially finished basement provides additional space for various uses, such as a recreation room, home office, or gym. One of the standout features is the like-new solar panel system, which is only one year old. These solar panels are a significant cost-saving addition, helping to lower your monthly energy expenses and reduce your carbon footprint. Don't miss the opportunity to make this wonderful property your new home! Contact us today to schedule a showing and experience the comfort and energy efficiency of 137 Benelli Dr for yourself.
